g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1daed15f35759aa8253d0b5ebcaaa5b5cb42b0e4","tid":114,"uid":7540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Long d其實真心問會唔會小別勝新婚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得捱得過就可以好長久 弊在大把人捱唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger<br />\n同埋都係講互相信任<br />\n見過好多long d 受唔住引誘出去偷食<br />\n最後分手搵過個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b01ec738173e3859e1077bc5b71a42c4e7e2e49","tid":114,"uid":10984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:52:58.000Z","msg":"Long d緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講個信字"},{"pid":"610c520c21d52e81bbc5d8f9c719359a2640c666","tid":114,"uid":7117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>LongD 唔夠3個月散左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係因為淡左？ take care</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話自己好忙冇時間拍拖<br />\n話自己要兼顧家人，學業，前途，音樂好大壓力好辛苦<br />\n拍之前以為自己準備好但發覺唔係<br />\n問佢仲中唔中意我佢都冇正面答了<br />\n應該係掛<br />\n<br />\n散左唔夠一個月"},{"pid":"5e2dabe3380b4eaeb08d5b0d5c0e44ee39c265a1","tid":114,"uid":2173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:38:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>LongD緊第6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會好似上面個巴打咁結埋婚！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係仲未決定到跟唔跟佢過去果邊定居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有得同居緊係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460353a4503229c301becd5623737f9807682783","tid":114,"uid":2173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"