smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee10f79ab34a466f1a2b2e8e304543f2788b318","tid":114,"uid":2173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>LongD 唔夠3個月散左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係因為淡左？ take care</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話自己好忙冇時間拍拖<br />\n話自己要兼顧家人，學業，前途，音樂好大壓力好辛苦<br />\n拍之前以為自己準備好但發覺唔係<br />\n問佢仲中唔中意我佢都冇正面答了<br />\n應該係掛<br />\n<br />\n散左唔夠一個月</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得我未準備好同佢LongD...唔係話唔信佢，而係過唔到自己心理關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e7bba62b3259e5d5d492b13e55337e88bc5711","tid":114,"uid":2173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Long d緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講個信字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要好好珍惜！"},{"pid":"26bfbb3ab37478de9ded988de679c3ca12bc6313","tid":114,"uid":2173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T20:07:49.000Z","msg":"女朋友就走，想送啲野比佢，但又唔想送機...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a53d0bab873fe6721a12b286a0ae1fbfeddbed1","tid":114,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T20:09:32.000Z","msg":"就黎有得見<br />\n仲差一個月咋<br />\n屌自己成日發脾氣真係仆街"},{"pid":"4f2971654acfd12966783ae940d2694db10ab3d7","tid":114,"uid":13534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T20:16:53.000Z","msg":"Long d 緊 女朋友比厹糾纏緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聖誕返去2-3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb0d0ab832cc4e0baabf27c0d2dc8049e8cfb90","tid":114,"uid":7117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T20:17:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>LongD 唔夠3個月散左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係因為淡左？ take care</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話自己好忙冇時間拍拖<br />\n話自己要兼顧家人，學業，前途，音樂好大壓力好辛苦<br />\n拍之前以為自己準備好但發覺唔係<br />\n問佢仲中唔中意我佢都冇正面答了<br />\n應該係掛<br />\n<br />\n散左唔夠一個月</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得我未準備好同佢LongD...唔係話唔信佢，而係過唔到自己心理關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係未準備好開始一段新關係<br />\n我同佢一齊左一個月就飛左去加拿大exchange一個sem<br />\n諗住12月22號趕返黎同佢過聖誕，但買左機票後幾個鐘佢同我講分手"},{"pid":"992346d7a8c00d9deeade7f66c871562a2407932","tid":114,"uid":14050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T20:31:52.000Z","msg":"我朋友上機前表白 到依加三個月仲好sweat"},{"pid":"28f12ee34e85cb8cc3909c5468215ebb30a2f6f6","tid":114,"uid":13534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T20:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>LongD 唔夠3個月散左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係因為淡左？ take care</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話自己好忙冇時間拍拖<br />\n話自己要兼顧家人，學業，前途，音樂好大壓力好辛苦<br />\n拍之前以為自己準備好但發覺唔係<br />\n問佢仲中唔中意我佢都冇正面答了<br />\n應該係掛<br />\n<br />\n散左唔夠一個月</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得我未準備好同佢LongD...唔係話唔信佢，而係過唔到自己心理關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係未準備好開始一段新關係<br />\n我同佢一齊左一個月就飛左去加拿大exchange一個sem<br />\n諗住12月22號趕返黎同佢過聖誕，但買左機票後幾個鐘佢同我講分手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照返去搏下啦"},{"pid":"33973f3299cfbde55ab70dbffbee05d5906d90bd","tid":114,"uid":3469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T20:54:38.000Z","msg":"Long d左1年幾，宜家仲一齊緊。<br />\n日日FaceTime"},{"pid":"f0af0ecb7a4ae789a9a327ec8af1d6dde04d4499","tid":114,"uid":7117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T22:13:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>LongD 唔夠3個月散左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係因為淡左？ take care</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話自己好忙冇時間拍拖<br />\n話自己要兼顧家人，學業，前途，音樂好大壓力好辛苦<br />\n拍